<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>(e)	The Game may also require at least one Character ID that You might, in part, be allowed to select subject to restrictions imposed in the reasonable discretion of NCsoft, including but not limited to the provisions of Section . You acknowledge that NCsoft may in its reasonable discretion modify any Character ID, any Team, Account ID, NCsoft Message Board ID, Character ID and/or Team designation, any characteristics related to a Character ID, or extend, limit or stop any communication or information on any Message Board. You additionally acknowledge that NCsoft has no ongoing and/or future duty to You regarding any license related to a modified or deleted Character ID.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>(f)	Additional Restrictions - You acknowledge You will not directly or indirectly, to the extent permitted by applicable law:</p>
