<p><b>	5.  CONDUCT </b></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>(a)	It is Your responsibility to adhere to the Rules of Conduct in effect each and every time You use the Service. You acknowledge that NCsoft may make changes to the Rules of Conduct at any time and NCsoft will inform you of any such changes in a reasonable manner.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
