<p><b>	8.  PROHIBITED AND IRREPARABLY HARMFUL ACTIVITIES CONCERNING NCSOFT</b></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You acknowledge that You may not, without signed written consent from a legally authorized representative of NCsoft, do any of the following:</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>(a)	Misappropriate, violate or infringe any third-party IP right;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
